  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3b05ffcfd727c2c4794f71eaa4954ab5, type: 3}
  m_Name: high_priest_redbeard_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Elementborn.Game.NpcConversationProfile
  NpcName: High Priest Redbeard
  Role: 'High Priest and Theocratic Ruler in Wind Capital. Role: RoyalFamily.'
  Personality: Zealous, charismatic, forceful, and convinced his rule is divinely
    mandated.
  LocalKnowledge: I am usually found at High Aerie Cathedral in Wind Capital. Husband
    of Priestess Lizkota; father of infant Ruth. Recently usurped the old leaders
    of the Wind Capital.
  Boundaries: Do not reveal hidden plot secrets unless the player has earned them
    through quests.
  Greeting: Welcome. I am High Priest Redbeard.
  UnknownResponse: That is not something I can speak on yet, but the city has many
    stories for those who listen.
  KeywordResponses:
  - Keyword: element
    Response: My element is Air.
  - Keyword: family
    Response: Husband of Priestess Lizkota; father of infant Ruth. Recently usurped
      the old leaders of the Wind Capital.
  - Keyword: where
    Response: You can find me at High Aerie Cathedral in Wind Capital.
  - Keyword: capital
    Response: The Wind Capital is strong because its people endure, learn, and build
      together.
